<tr>
<th style="background:#b08261; color:#fee8ab; text-align:center; font-size:larger;">Sephardi Jews<br />
יהדות ספרד (<i>Yahadut Sfarad</i>)</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border:none; padding:0.6em 0 0 0;">
<div style="margin-top:1px; margin-bottom:1px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Sephardi_Jews_-_mosaic.PNG" class="image" title="Sephardi Jews - mosaic.PNG"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/60/Sephardi_Jews_-_mosaic.PNG/300px-Sephardi_Jews_-_mosaic.PNG" width="300" height="191" border="0" /></a>
<div style="background-color:#fee8ab">
<p><small>1<sup>st</sup> row: <a href="/wiki/Maimonides" title="Maimonides">Maimonides</a>•<a href="/wiki/Isaac_Abrabanel" title="Isaac Abrabanel">Isaac Abrabanel</a>•<a href="/wiki/Baruch_Spinoza" title="Baruch Spinoza">Baruch Spinoza</a>•<a href="/wiki/David_Nieto" title="David Nieto">David Nieto</a>•<a href="/wiki/Daniel_Mendoza" title="Daniel Mendoza">Daniel Mendoza</a>•<a href="/wiki/David_Ricardo" title="David Ricardo">David Ricardo</a><br />
2<sup>nd</sup> row: <a href="/wiki/Moses_Montefiore" title="Moses Montefiore">Moses Montefiore</a>•<a href="/wiki/Benjamin_Disraeli" title="Benjamin Disraeli">Benjamin Disraeli</a>•<a href="/wiki/Sabato_Morais" title="Sabato Morais">Sabato Morais</a>•<a href="/wiki/Emma_Lazarus" title="Emma Lazarus">Emma Lazarus</a>•<a href="/wiki/Benjamin_N._Cardozo" title="Benjamin N. Cardozo">Benjamin Cardozo</a>•<a href="/wiki/David_de_Sola_Pool" title="David de Sola Pool">David de Sola Pool</a><br /></small></p>
<small>3<sup>rd</sup> row: <a href="/wiki/Basil_Henriques" title="Basil Henriques">Basil Henriques</a>•<a href="/wiki/Pierre_Mend%C3%A8s-France" title="Pierre Mendès-France" class="mw-redirect">Pierre Mendès-France</a>•<a href="/wiki/Sam_Costa" title="Sam Costa">Sam Costa</a>•<a href="/wiki/Jacques_Derrida" title="Jacques Derrida">Jacques Derrida</a>•<a href="/wiki/Shlomo_Amar" title="Shlomo Amar">Shlomo Amar</a>•<a href="/wiki/Hank_Azaria" title="Hank Azaria">Hank Azaria</a></small></div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border:none; padding:0.3em 0 0.6em 0; line-height:11pt; font-size:95%;"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="background:#fee8ab;">Total population</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<p><b>Sephardi Jews</b><br />
<b>1.5 - 2.0 million (estimate)<sup class="noprint Template-Fact"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources&#160;since December 2008" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed">citation needed</a></i>]</span></sup></b><br />
<small>up to 20% of the total 'Jewish World' population</small></p>
</td>
</tr>
